      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t有点意思。这是刚刚在匪伪“百度”网上搜“品葱”（带引号）的结果首页：<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS8yTFFsakZuLnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/2LQljFn.png\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/2LQljFn.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/2LQljFn.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\n在此首页搜索结果中，“品葱为什么不封—虎观百科” 及 “据环球网披露：品葱是一个讨论各种问题的….” 两条搜索结果点击进去都是“404 结果不存在”之类。但那条 “他们明目张胆地造谣，还嘲笑中国人的智商！是什么来头？中华网” 搜索结果点击进去有对品葱网的一些讨论：<br/>\n<a href=\"url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly8zZy5jaGluYS5jb20vYWN0L21pbGl0YXJ5LzU2OC8yMDIwMDIyMS8zNzgyNTY2Ny5odG1s\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://3g.china.com/act/military/568/20200221/37825667.html\">https://3g.china.com/act/military/568/20200221/37825667.html</a>，是这个“中华网”网页内在讨论：<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9YTjZ2NU1rLnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/XN6v5Mk.png\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/XN6v5Mk.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/XN6v5Mk.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\n其余搜索结果都是关于烹调做菜选名字等无关“品葱”网的内容。\t\t</div>",
